verse.lines:
{lang-eng}There’s a fountain flowing deep and wide,
Flowing now in you and me;
In it God is fully satisfied!
There’s a fountain flowing deep and wide.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Every morning I come to that fount;
Oh, the cleansing that I need!
All the sins I’ve lost I cannot count
In that fountain flowing deep and wide!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}All day long the thirsting in me grows;
Deeper, wider still I drink.
With the saints today I’ll overflow
In that fountain flowing deep and wide!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Saints of God, now let your praises swell;
Let the waters freely flow;
For together He among us dwells —
Christ, the fountain flowing deep and wide!{/lang-eng}
